{"tid":1384040,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又要拉一個出嚟打靶","createTime":"2019-07-29T23:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T18:40:59.000Z","uid":130394,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6ac863d7ea3001efdb071d1c71a409c54e5ddead","tid":1384040,"uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mriphts.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMriphts.jpg&h=7f2cbef9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解我要po呢個咁可愛嘅肥仔出嚟呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係因為呢個冚家剷死十次都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vg2xrm5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvg2xrm5.jpg&h=1adde54f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁多位出街影撚住佢呀<br />\n個人已經夠戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前梁繼平未公開自己個樣嘅時候, 佢已經將沖立法會冇打格嘅人啲相Share曬出嚟. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KwAGjJo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKwAGjJo.jpg&h=4cbf5adc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嗱！死肥鬼我冇屈你㗎！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JfcmjJJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJfcmjJJ.jpg&h=998e3af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好人好姐香港出世,仲好鍾意睇埋啲垃圾大陸新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFacebook見到屌撚完佢仲要即刻block咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位知道點樣問候佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&lt;b&gt;<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span>&lt;/b&gt;<br />\n&lt;b&gt;<span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span>&lt;/b